wikipedia_page.main: Aicha Alicia McKenzie (born February, 1977) is a former female British gymnast, model and dancer who is also the CEO of AMCK Management, which founded AMCK Dance in 2005, AMCK Models in 2008 and AMCK Fit in June 2017.
